text: Lamb Weston is an American food processing company. It is one of the world's largest producers and processors of frozen french fries, waffle fries, and other frozen potato products. It is headquartered in Eagle, Idaho. The company was founded in 1950. == Other websites == * Official website Category:American food companies Category:Companies based in Idaho Category:1950 establishments in the United States Category:20th-century establishments in Idaho
